tourBios.otherInfo: Won the 2011 Canadian Collegiate Athletic Association Championships while attending Humber College, Finished second at the Ontario Collegiate Athletic Association Championships.
tourBios.prYrSeason: Regained non-exempt status with rounds of 76-75-75-70 at the 2012 Fall Q- School, Made two cuts in his rookie season in 2012, with his best finish a tie for 50th at the Times Colonist Island Savings Open, Earned exempt status with rounds of 76-74-72-72 at the 2012 California Q-School

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T50th in 2012 at the Times Colonist Island Savings Open.
